{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017t2kRBeedovDmqtrAhQMaW","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→@use \"palette\" as *;\n     2→\n     3→// ============================================================\n     4→// Bar toggle button\n     5→// ============================================================\n     6→\n     7→.notif-toggle-wrap {\n     8→  position: relative;\n     9→}\n    10→\n    11→// Flat-top hexagon badge (Chrysaki status indicator shape)\n    12→.notif-badge {\n    13→  clip-path: polygon(25% 0%, 75% 0%, 100% 50%, 75% 100%, 25% 100%, 0% 50%);\n    14→  background: $error;\n    15→  color: $text-primary;\n    16→  font-size: 9px;\n    17→  font-weight: bold;\n    18→  min-width: 16px;\n    19→  min-height: 16px;\n    20→  padding: 0px 2px;\n    21→}\n    22→\n    23→// ============================================================\n    24→// Panel window (glassmorphism — compositor blur provides depth)\n    25→// ============================================================\n    26→\n    27→.notif-panel {\n    28→  background-color: rgba(15, 17, 23, 0.15);\n    29→  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n    30→  box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n    31→  padding: 10px;\n    32→  min-width: 320px;\n    33→  max-width: 400px;\n    34→}\n    35→\n    36→// --- Panel header ---\n    37→\n    38→.notif-panel-header {\n    39→  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n    40→  padding-bottom: 6px;\n    41→  margin-bottom: 4px;\n    42→}\n    43→\n    44→.notif-panel-title {\n    45→  color: $text-primary;\n    46→  font-size: 15px;\n    47→  font-weight: bold;\n    48→  padding: 4px 0px;\n    49→}\n    50→\n    51→.notif-clear-all-btn {\n    52→  background: transparent;\n    53→  border: none;\n    54→  color: $text-muted;\n    55→  font-size: 11px;\n    56→  padding: 2px 6px;\n    57→  min-width: 0px;\n    58→\n    59→  &:hover {\n    60→    color: $error;\n    61→  }\n    62→}\n    63→\n   